Tyemet ne po kayaneetap Abraham


1   Kingo pata tuguuchooto, kotyem `Kamuktaindet Abraham, koleenji, “Abraham” ak ki le, “Ami yu.” 
2   Koleenji, “Imut weeriing'ung', nooto ne ineegei, ne ichame, Isak, ak iwe agoi emetap Moriah, si igoite eng' olooto koek kagoochinet ne kibeelei eng' tulweet age ne tuun amwaun.” 
3  Ara king'eet Abraham karon miising' komusta, ki iito kiit ne kitebee eng' sigiryennyi si kobiit kolaany, ak ki imut murenik aeng' eng' che ki tinyei, koba kobooto ineendet ak Isak weeriinnyi. Ki pet kweenik che po kagoochinet ne kibeelei, yeityo koba ole kiga koarorchi Kamuktaindet. 
4  Ki tabendo Abraham eng' peetuut ne po somok ak ki keer koronooto kota ko loo. 
5  Yeityo koleenji `Abraham murenjoto chiget, “Otebi eng' yu kobooto sigiryet, ak keebe oliin ak weeri, si kesaa, ak keweigei kogeny.” 
6  Ki nam Abraham kweenik che po kagoochinet ne kibeelei ak koganapchi Isak weeriinnyi. Ki ip ineendet eng' eunnyi maat ak rotweet ak koba tuwai. 
7  Ki ng'alaalji anyun `Isak kwandanyi Abraham, koleenji, “Abba!” Ak ki le, “Ami yu, weeriinnyu.” Ak ki le, “Keero, mi yu maat ak kweenik, ago mi ano aarwetap kechir ne egu kagoochinet ne kibeelei?” 
8  Ki leenji Abraham, “Weeriinnyu, cheeng'jingei Kamuktaindet aarwetap keechiir ne egu kagoochinet ne kibeelei.” Yeityo koba tuwai.


9   Ye kingo it koronooto ole kiga koarorchi Kamuktaindet, koteech Abraham kaptisisyet eng' olooto. Kitet kweenik, yeityo korat weeriinnyi Isak, ak konde ineendet kweenik parak eng' kaptisisyet. 
10  Ki iyogoito anyun eunnyi Abraham, konam rotweet koleen kobare weeriinnyi. 
11  Ago kiguur anyun ineendet `malaikayatap Kamuktaindet ne Toroor eng' kipsengwet koleenji, “Abraham, Abraham!” Kole, “Ami yu.” 
12  Koleenji, “Ametwaa lakweet, ameyachi kiy tugul, amu kaanai nguno ale igonyiti Kamuktaindet, amu ma ieteno weeriing'ung', ne weeriing'ung' ne ineegei.” 
13  Kotabendo Abraham ak koguskong'; ogeero, mengit ne kanam sondiit kuinoikyik. Ki wo anyun Abraham koget mengit ak koeny koek kogoochinet ne kibeelei, kogeere weeriinnyi. 
14  Ak ki kuuree Abraham yooto, “Koonu Kamuktaindet ne Toroor;” ko uu ye kimwaei agoi kora, keele, “Kigonune tulweetap Kamuktaindet.” 
15  Ak ki kuur ne po aeng' `malaikaiyatap Kamuktaindet ne Toroor Abraham eng' kipsengwet, 
16   koleenji, “Kayosyechigei aneege, mwaei Kamuktaindet ne Toroor, amu keyai kii, ma ieteno weeriing'ung' ne ineegei. 
17   Eng' kaberuret aberuurin, ak eng' kayabet ayabi iyoteng'ung' kobarait kotenit kecheik che po kipsengwet, ak kotenit ng'aniek che po ngeguutap nyanjet. Tuun nyabani lagoguk kurgeetap puunikwak; 
18   ak tuun kiberuuri pororyosyek tugul che po ng'wony eng' keswondeng'ung'; amu kegas iit kutinnyu.” 
19  Ak ki weigei anyun Abraham kwo ole mi murenjugachiget, ak ki ng'eetyo koba tugul agoi Beer-sheba, ak ki meny Abraham olooto.


20  Kingo pata tuguuchuuto, kemwachi Abraham keleenji, “Keero, kogosikyi Milkah agine ng'eetap kamenng'ung' Nahor lagok: 
21  lakweet ne po tai ko Us, ng'eetap kamet ko Bus, Kemuel kwandap Aram; 
22  Kesed, Haso, Pildas, Jidlap, ak Bethuel.” 
23  (Ak ki sich `Bethuel Rebeka). Chuuto sisiit ko ki sikyi Milkah Nahor ng'eetap kametap Abraham. 
24  Ak ki sikyi Reuma chebaigeiyandennyi Teba, Gaham, Tahas, ak Maaka.

